            <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">S·ª± ki·ªán c√¥ng khai</h2> 

            <p className="text-gray-600 mb-6">Tham gia b√¨nh ch·ªçn c√°c s·ª± ki·ªán c√¥ng khai</p> 

            <div className="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3"> 

